                },
                "text_xUQqfM": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>A classic summer staple originally designed for rock climbers back in the 80s, the Gramicci G Shorts are designed to be rugged and hard wearing while still being comfortable for active and daily wear. </p><p>They feature a diamond shaped crotch gusset for mobility and a built in nylon belt you can pull with one hand for adjusting on the the climbing wall.</p><p></p><p>A favourite pick for all the staff here every time summer comes around.</p><p>Available now in a wide range of colours</p>",
                    "width": "fit-content",
                    "max_width": "normal",
